Package: tasker
Type: Package
Title: Task and Pipeline Execution Tracking
Version: 0.6.0
Date: 2026-01-14
Authors@R: person('Gregory', 'Warnes', email = 'greg@warnes.net', role = c('aut', 'cre'))
Description: Track the status and progress of tasks, subtasks, and pipeline
    executions in a PostgreSQL database. Provides functions for initializing,
    updating, and querying task execution status with support for hierarchical
    tracking (stages, tasks, subtasks) and detailed progress monitoring. 
    Supports automatic script detection and database lookup of stage/task names.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    DBI,
    dplyr,
    dbplyr,
    yaml,
    bbcDB,
    this.path
Suggests:
    RPostgres,
    RSQLite,
    RMariaDB,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    mockery
